# readbro

Single MCP for file reads. **Never use built-in Read, Grep, SemanticSearch, or Glob for code you can reach via readbro.**

| Tool | When |
|------|------|
| `read_file` | All file reads — **layer L1 default** (not L3). `path` is string **or array** — batch in ONE call |
| `search_symbol` | Named symbol/class/function/use-case — **NOT grep/rg**. `target` or `targets`, optional `path`, `budget: 4000` |
| `blast_radius` | Before editing non-trivial source |
| `session_status` | Repo health snapshot (totals, efficiency) |
| `session_gain` | Where savings come from (top files, globs) |
| `session_clear` | Clear repo cache |

**Do not** grep/rg/SemanticSearch/Glob to find named symbols or read source — use `search_symbol` / `read_file`.

grep/Glob only for: filename discovery, regex/text patterns, or things readbro cannot do.

**L3 = full raw** — avoid for exploration; auto-capped to 200 lines. `max_lines: -1` = full file (only when you truly need full raw).

Full guide: `~/.agents/skills/readbro/SKILL.md`
